n Untersuchung auf Basis der Genogrammarbeit.  afunded by Land Steiermark, Referat Wissenschaft und Forschung  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 4aArbeit. 4aArbeits- und Industriesoziologie. 4aCare-Ökonomien. 4aCommunity Supported Agriculture. 4aFood Studies. 4aGenogrammarbeit. 4aKonventionalisierung. 4aKulturanthropologie. 4aMassenproduktion. 4aNachhaltigkeit. 4aNatur. 4aSoziologie. 4aUmwelt. 4aUmweltsoziologie. 4aWirtschaft. 4aÖsterreich. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh  aAustria.  aCare Economies.  aCommunity Supported Agriculture.  aConventionalization.  aCultural Anthropology.  aEconomy.  aEnvironment.  aEnvironmental Sociology.  aFood Studies.  aGenogram Work.  aMass Production.  aNature.  aSociology of Work and Industry.  aSociology.  aSustainability.  aWork.1 aHeistinger, Andrea, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKosnik, Elisabeth, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKosnik, Elisabeth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSorgo, Gabriele, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aSorgo, Gabriele, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb2 aLand Steiermark, Referat Wissenschaft und Forschungefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021